 new CookieContainer().Add(cookie);
 ```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="450bc-171">コンマ文字は、同じ行の個別の cookie 間の区切り記号として使用されます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="450bc-171">The comma character is used as a delimiter between separate cookies on the same line.</span></span>
